my-rebounds-start-2024-property-drag-continues?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“所有民族都很重要”：新的中国教科书引用西方的分裂来证明北京的融合政策合理</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3255567/all-ethnic-groups-matter-new-chinese-textbook-cites-splits-west-justify-beijings-integration?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>分析人士预计，随着北京不再强调少数民族的独特品质，针对少数民族的平权行动将进一步取消。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 23:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3255567/all-ethnic-groups-matter-new-chinese-textbook-cites-splits-west-justify-beijings-integration?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国对高科技、先进行业的关注可能是经济复苏的关键</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3255483/chinas-focus-hi-tech-advanced-sectors-could-hold-key-revival?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国对创新驱动发展的新关注为可持续发展和避免中等收入陷阱带来了希望。先进领域的技术突破可能成为改变国家未来并与美国并驾齐驱的决定性驱动力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 21:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3255483/chinas-focus-hi-tech-advanced-sectors-could-hold-key-revival?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国议员表示，由于担心中国间谍活动而禁止应用程序，字节跳动投资者可能会在 TikTok 销售中获胜</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-war/article/3255721/bytedance-investors-could-win-tiktok-sale-says-republican-lawmaker?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>国会议员迈克·加拉格尔表示，强制出售符合字节跳动投资者的经济利益。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 19:31:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-war/article/3255721/bytedance-investors-could-win-tiktok-sale-says-republican-lawmaker?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国正在花费数十亿美元建设国家计算网络。其数据负责人说出了原因</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3255710/china-spending-billions-national-computing-network-its-data-chief-says-why?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>刘烈宏阐述了在“东方数据、西方计算”大型项目中全面整合国家计算能力的案例。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 14:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLi